    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "<span class=\"sentence\" id=\"0\" type=\"start\">&star;</span>לְכַתְּחִלָּה אוֹ דִיעֲבַד? תָּא שְׁמַע, דְּתָנֵי <span class=\"name-reference-marker name-reference-amora\" data-sage-type=\"amora\" title=\"Rav Naḥman, fifth-generation Amora.\" data-authority-id=\"993\" data-full-name=\"Rav Naḥman\" data-name-he=\"רב זביד\">רַב זְבִיד</span> בַּר",
      "segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "אוֹשַׁעְיָא: הַלּוֹקֵחַ קַנְקַנִּים מִן הַגּוֹיִם —",
      "segment_ids": [
