      "text": "בְּעָלְמָא הוּא. <span class=\"sentence\" id=\"4\" type=\"start\">&star;</span><span class=\"name-reference-marker name-reference-amora\" data-sage-type=\"amora\" title=\"Rabbi Yitzḥak bar Nappaḥa II, third-generation Amora.\" data-authority-id=\"1885\" data-full-name=\"Rabbi Yitzḥak bar Nappaḥa II\" data-name-he=\"רבי יצחק\">רַב יִצְחָק</span> בַּר בִּיסְנָא הֲוָה לֵיהּ",
