    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "בְּשִׁימְשָׁא, פְּקַעוּ. אֲמַר לֵיהּ <span class=\"name-reference-marker name-reference-amora\" data-sage-type=\"amora\" title=\"Rabbi Akiva I, second-generation Amora.\" data-authority-id=\"6\" data-full-name=\"Rabbi Akiva I\" data-name-he=\"רבי אבא\">רַבִּי אַבָּא</span>: אֲסַרְתִּינְהוּ עֲלָךְ",
