      "width": "380px",
      "text": "מַיָּא, אַנּוֹחֵי בְּשִׁימְשָׁא מִי אֲמוּר? <span class=\"sentence\" id=\"5\" type=\"start\">&star;</span>אָמַר <span class=\"name-reference-marker name-reference-amora\" data-sage-type=\"amora\" title=\"Rabbi Yusna, fifth-generation Amora.\" data-authority-id=\"1761\" data-full-name=\"Rabbi Yusna\" data-name-he=\"רבי יוסנא\">רַבִּי יוֹסְנָא</span> אָמַר רַבִּי",
