      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 33b:2:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "דשליח שויה ותנן (לקמן",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 33b:2:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 33b:2:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "דף",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 33b:2:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "לה.) שילח",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 33b:2:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "ביד בנו ביד",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 33b:2:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "עבדו פטור הכא עדיף שיש לו",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 33b:2:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "כח להוציא ממון",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 33b:2:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "כמו לבעלים עצמן וא\"ת אכתי",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 33b:2:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "תקשי הא מנה לפלוני",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 33b:2:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "ביד",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 33b:2:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "פלוני",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 33b:2:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "ובא",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 33b:2:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "בלא הרשאה",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 33b:2:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 33b:2:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "חייבין",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 33b:2:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "דומיא",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 33b:2:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "דכהן דלא",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 33b:2:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "שייך הרשאה ואר\"י דיתור משנה",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 33b:2:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "אתא",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 33b:2:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 33b:2:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "לאשמועינן דוקא בכה\"ג פטור בכל ענין",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 33b:2:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "דלא משכחת חיובא אבל",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 33b:2:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "מנה לפלוני",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 33b:2:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "ביד פלוני זימנין",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 33b:2:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "דמשכח חיובא",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 33b:2:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "כמו בבא בהרשאה <big><b>היכא</b></big>. ואיירי",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 33b:2:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "שאחר",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 33b:2:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "שכתב לו",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 33b:2:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "הרשאה כפר לו ולמ\"ד",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 33b:2:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 33b:2:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "במרובה (<a href=\"/bava_kamma/70a\">ב&quot;ק דף ע.</a>)",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 33b:2:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "אפילו לא",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 33b:2:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "כפר ליה",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 33b:2:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "לא כתבינן מוקמינן מתני'",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 33b:2:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "דהכא בפקדון דהא טעמא",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 33b:2:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 33b:2:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "דלא כתבינן מפרש",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 33b:2:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "התם משום",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 33b:2:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "דגזל ולא",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 33b:2:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 33b:2:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "נתייאשו",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 33b:2:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 33b:2:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "הבעלים שניהן אין",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 33b:2:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "יכולין",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 33b:2:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "להקדיש ופקדון יכול",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 33b:2:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "להקדיש כדמוכח התם דמייתי עלה",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 33b:2:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "לעיל (<a href=\"/avodah_zarah/69b\">דף סט:</a>) לסייעתא",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 33b:2:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "מהא דתנן",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 33b:2:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "930px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "אין הגונב אחר הגנב משלם תשלומי כפל ובפקדון",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 33b:2:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "930px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "משלם כדתנן בפ' המפקיד (<a href=\"/bava_metzia/33b\">ב&quot;מ דף לג:</a>)",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 33b:2:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "930px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "וכן מוכח בהמוכר את הספינה (<a href=\"/bava_batra/88a\">ב&quot;ב דף פח.</a>)",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 33b:2:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "930px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "גבי ההוא גברא דאייתי קארי לפום",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 33b:2:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "930px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "נהרא אתו כ\"ע שקול חדא חדא ואמר הרי הם מקודשים לשמים ומסקינן דאי לאו דקיצי דמייהו קדשי",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 33b:2:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "930px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "דברשותא דמרייהו קיימי א\"נ איכא לאוקומא במקרקעי",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 33b:2:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "930px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "דודאי כתבינן ליה דקרקע אינה נגזלת וכמ\"ד",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 33b:2:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "930px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "לקמן פרק שבועת הפקדון (<a href=\"/shevuot/37b\">דף לז:</a>) המשביע עדי קרקע חייב והא דלא משני הש\"ס",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 33b:2:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "930px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "הכי דהוה ניחא לכולהו לישני משום דלא חייש לשנויי",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 33b:2:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "930px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "אלא לפי לשון שתופס עיקר מיהו קשה בפרק יש",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 33b:2:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "930px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "בכור (<a href=\"/bekhorot/48b\">בכורות דף מח:</a>) גבי ב' נשים של ב' אנשים שלא ביכרו וילדו",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 33b:2:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "930px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "שני זכרים",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 33b:2:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "930px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "מת אחד מהן בתוך ל' יום אם לכהן אחד נתנו יחזור להן ה' סלעים ומוקי לה בבא בהרשאה",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 33b:2:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "930px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "והתם לא שייך לא פקדון ולא קרקע דאין פודין בקרקעות",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 33b:2:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "930px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "מיהו התם נמי איכא לשנויי בבא במעמד שלשתן ור\"ת",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 33b:2:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "930px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "פוסק דכתבינן אפילו אמטלטלי דכפריה דטעמא דלא כתבינן מפרש משום",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 33b:2:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "930px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "דמיחזי כשיקרא (ובפרק כל הגט (גיטין דף כו: ושם) ובהכותב (כתובות דף פה. ושם) מסקינן דלמיחזי לשיקרא לא חיישינן ואין",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 33b:2:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "930px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "להאריך כאן בדבר) <big><b>ונאמר</b></big>. תימה כיון דגמרי' מפקדון ניבעי בהלואה ובעושק ייחוד כלי כדאמרינן גבי שבועת",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 33b:2:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "930px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "הפקדון בהזהב (<a href=\"/bava_metzia/48a\">ב&quot;מ דף מח.</a>) <big><b>אואין</b></big>. דעיקר לא אתי להפסידה כתובתה אלא להשקותה",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 33b:2:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    }
  ]
}